title: Holden Commodore
summary: The Holden Commodore is a large family car that was sold by Holden from 1978 to 2020. It was manufactured from 1978 to 2017 in Australia and from 1979 to 1990 in New Zealand, with production of the locally manufactured versions in Australia ending on 20 October 2017.[2] Sales of the Commodore ended in 2020, coinciding with the discontinuation of the Holden brand and nameplate entirely.[3]
